# 📊 Retirement Calculator Automation (Playwright)

This project automates the testing of the Securian Retirement Calculator using Playwright with JavaScript and Page Object Model (POM) design.

---

## 🚀 Project Overview

- Automates retirement calculator workflows
- Uses Playwright Test Runner
- Implements Page Object Model (POM)
- Covers form filling, toggles, and submission flow

---

## 📁 Project Structure
.
├── pageObject/
