## 🧪 Test Scenarios

- Fill required fields
- Toggle social security options
- Submit retirement form
- Update and verify values

---

## 🧱 Page Object Model

Class: `PensionOrbital`

Methods:
- `navigate()` → Open application
- `fillCore()` → Fill form data
- `updateFillCore()` → Update values
- `toggleSocialTrue/False()` → Handle toggles
- `submit()` → Submit form
- `isResultVisible()` → Verify results

